name: Daisies N Lace Pet Vest (XS)
description:
This vest is designed with a yellow cotton embroidered fabric, trimmed with lace, harness ring, velcro belly and neck fasteners, and finished with a fabric and lacy daisy. This vest will turn heads as she swishes along her route or just to keep her a bit warm during walks and outings.

name: Lovely Lady Green Embroidered Pet Dress (XS)
description:
Your little girl will pull your heart strings when she wears this sweet little outfit. Lots of frilly girl in this dress. This dress features white soft cotton with green flower embroidery skirt and bodice trimmed in eyelet lace with a beautiful fabric bow with a green ribbon flowing down the skirt to compliment. Velcro closures complete the ensemble. A harness ring has been added for the saftey of your pet. This dress is completely lined for the comfort of your little girl.

name: Party Pink Couture Pet Dress (XS)
description:
Luxury dog clothing by Tiny Paws Designs for the pampered pet. This Grand Entrance design is a soft pink eyelet. The bodice is self-lined for comfort. The skirt of the dress is self-lined, has a layer of tulle to provide more fullness, and a second self-lined skirt of contrasting white cotton fabric with pink polka-dots trimmed in lace. The dress has a D-ring tab sewn in for a matching leash. The double collar has a self-lined, lace trimmed cotton collar with a lace collar overlay. Velcro closures complete the belly and neck. This beautiful dress will be the talk of the grooming parlor. 


Need sizing help, visit my guide http://www.tinypawsdesigns.com/size.html

name: Pink Beret Pet Hat (XS)
description:
Your little lady will be right in style with this pink eyelet, self lined, lace trimmed hat. This hat fits best over the ear and is held in place with a gentle elastic band. Our model loves it and runs around getting ooohs and aaahs from everyone who see's her. Your pampered pet will be noticed in the Couture Dog Clothing. She will make a Grand Entrance wearing this Tiny Paws Designs item.


This hat is an extra small size. It is shown on a 4 lb Yorkshire Terrer. I also have a 2.5 lb Yorkie Male, Matisse', and I use him to model my extra extra small designs. The hat also fits him nicely.
